{"tid":1981887,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"CNN：金正恩接受手術後病危","createTime":"2020-04-21T02:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T03:48:29.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9610b14252a486522c4a4f93cfbe806d1d34b3ff","tid":1981887,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:25:11.000Z","msg":"2020-04-21 10:06:23<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕北韓領導人金正恩有菸癮且體格肥胖，健康問題一直是外界關注議題。近日他因缺席北韓重大慶典「太陽節」，再度引起揣測。據消息指出，金正恩是接受心血管疾病手術，且術後復原良好。如今卻有外媒報導，金正恩在術後情況「非常危急」。<br />\n<br />\n「太陽節」為北韓前金日成誕辰紀念日，金正恩卻罕見缺席，是2012年上任以來首次。後經脫北者所經營的《每日北韓》報導，金正恩在金氏家族專用醫院、平安北道妙香山的香山治療所進行手術，由平壤金萬有醫院、北韓紅十字醫院、平壤醫科大學附屬醫院的頂尖醫生聯合操刀。<br />\n<br />\n《CNN》報導，美國官方知情人士指出，金正恩在接受手術後情況非常為危險，但尚無進一步資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3140295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3140295&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzX88up93QrsUiEJqOxYGoBw%3D&h=ebdabd71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3140295&h=0d687743\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3140295</a>"},{"pid":"b79b1eff3c281f36e143a09083a8301c6692d3c0","tid":1981887,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:29:48.000Z","msg":"全北韓最肥既金正恩竟然出事 你有咩恭賀說話想講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FK53R0fnH-E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFK53R0fnH-E&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzX88up93QrsUiEJqOxYGoBw%3D&h=8ac0678e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FK53R0fnH-E</a>"},{"pid":"cd3a6818dc567f102f3469966c91973930835c43","tid":1981887,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:35:18.000Z","msg":"如果金仔出事班所謂頂尖醫生會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces